name: Dead Precedence - #37 Richard Nixon
description: Dead Precedence is a series of algorithmic paintings which use history, found images and time to produce a portrait of lineage to an American President. Each presidential portrait made by the layering of previous figureheads. Painted in iterations correlating in years since death. Info: ryanthompson.name/project-dead-precedence. By Ryan Thompson - 2021 | 2400 x 2800 pixels.
